   visual analysis skills in my Japanese Visual Culture class. The in-class
   exercises outlined here teach students to examine the media they
   love-manga-through the lens of context, both historical and visual. By
   challenging students to closely read images and various forms of media,
   this pedagogy works to help students expand their understanding of
