   Faster categorization of documents is required in forensic investigation
   but analysis of these documents is very difficult. So, there is a need
   to separate multiple collections of documents into similar ones through
   clustering. Specifying number of clusters is mandatory in existing
   partitioning algorithms and the output is totally dependent on given
