   language barrier and translation ambiguity are two challenging issues
   for cross-lingual document representation. To this end, we propose to
   represent cross-lingual documents through statistical word senses, which
   are automatically discovered from a parallel corpus through a novel
   cross-lingual word sense induction model and a sense clustering method.
