   relation to clustering. However, Semi-NMF has been found to perform
   somewhat less than NMF, in terms of clustering, when applied to positive
   data such as text, which we focus on. Inspired by the recent success of
   neural word embedding models, e.g., word2vec, in learning high quality
   real valued vector representations of words, we propose to integrate a
   word embedding model into Semi-NMF. This allows Semi-NMF to capture more
   semantic relationships among words and, thereby, to infer document
