   been studied and applied in many different fields, including pattern
   recognition, data mining, decision science and statistics. Clustering
   algorithms can be mainly classified as hierarchical and partitional
   clustering approaches. Partitioning around medoids (PAM) is a
   partitional clustering algorithms, which is less sensitive to outliers,
   but greatly affected by the poor initialization of medoids. In this
