   of clusters is always returned in every run of the algorithm. Thus, the
   use of the proposed algorithm significantly reduces the possibility of
   k-means converging to a locally optimal solution. The paper explores the
   genetic algorithm framework to obtain the original seed points and
   couples this with the use of the differential evolution heuristic to
