   such information with the semantically better result. In this paper, we
   propose a framework of lightweight semantic-based medical document
   retrieval in Bahasa Indonesia. The medical information is focused on
   diagnosis, etiology, epidemiology, clinical manifestation, and
   guidelines. The framework firstly annotates queries' by using the
   ontology, analyse the information networks within the ontology and
   extracts the context of the queries. When a query falls within one
