   distance that allows to efficiently compare objects of different nature.
   Recently, a new promising metric called Word Mover's Distance was
   proposed to measure the divergence between text passages. In this paper,
   we demonstrate that this metric can be extended to incorporate
   term-weighting schemes and provide more accurate and computationally
