   resources should be available, readable and understandable. In semantic
   web, the ontology plays a central role for the information retrieval,
   which use to retrieves more relevant information from unstructured
   information. This paper presents a semantic-based retrieval system for
   the Arabic text, which expands the input query semantically using Arabic
   domain ontology. In the proposed approach, the search engine index is
   represented using Vector Space Model (VSM), and the Arabic's place nouns
   domain ontology has been used which constructed and implemented using
