   retrieval is the fundamental and important issue to search information
   under the scenario of ``Big Data{''}. Some recent works have proposed
   neural information retrieval, which has a significant improvement in
   terms of some problems (e.g., semantic gap). However, such retrieval
   takes a general-purposed query rather than event-oriented query as the
