   construction (AEC) projects and fast track execution of project works,
   written documents are becoming more and more important for project
   coordination, communication, and works control. Finding all the relevant
   information from unstructured construction documents is critical to
   various management tasks such as work planning, progress control, and
   claims. A framework is proposed in this research to retrieve
   project-wide as-needed information from AEC documents. Through this
   framework, improvement in the levels of precision and recall in the
   information retrieval process can be made effective through the use of a
