   retrieve a ranked list of (text) documents from a fixed corpus in
   response to free-form keyword queries. In this work, the query and
   documents are modeled by enhanced graph based representations. Ranking
   features are generated by matching the two representations through
   semantic similarity measures which consider both semantic and
